<emphasis bold="true" box="[166,401,768,802]" pageId="159" pageNumber="762">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Rwenzori Shaggy Rats are nocturnal and diurnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[168,1107,812,841]" pageId="159" pageNumber="762" type="biology_ecology">
